---
title: Pork & Apple Burgers with Rosemary Fries & Garlic Aioli
description: You know what’s cool? Yeah, that’s right – burgers. You know what else is cool? Mixing up a fast food classic with the sophisticated combination of pork and crunchy apple. In fact, you may as well put on your sunglasses at night right now, because you just became the coolest cat in the neighbourhood.
